We finally got
a piece of the pie

00:23.816 --> 00:26.405
Fish don't fry
in the kitchen

00:26.543 --> 00:29.029
Beans don't burn
on the grill

00:29.167 --> 00:31.652
Took a whole lot of tryin'

00:31.790 --> 00:34.206
Just to get up that hill

00:34.344 --> 00:36.829
Now we're up
in the big leagues

00:36.967 --> 00:39.384
Gettin' our turn at bat

00:39.522 --> 00:42.007
As long as we live,
it's you and me, baby

00:42.145 --> 00:43.767
There ain't nothin' wrong
with that

00:43.905 --> 00:46.494
We're movin' on up
Movin' on up

